-- ==============================================================================
-- SCRIPT NAME: quarterly_marketing_vs_payers
-- VERSION: v1.0
-- AUTHOR: Adi B.
-- CREATED: 2025-01-01
--
-- PURPOSE:
-- Track marketing spend, number of payers, and number of first-time depositors
-- per custom fiscal quarter to support growth and accounting analysis.
--
-- DESCRIPTION:
-- - Defines custom fiscal quarters (Q1 = Augâ€“Oct, Q2 = Novâ€“Jan, etc.)
-- - Aggregates marketing spend from APPSFLYER_XPEND_DATA
-- - Aggregates unique payers from PAYMENTS table by payment date
-- - Extracts FTDs by selecting each user's first-ever payment date
-- - Joins all components using `custom_quarter`
--
-- USAGE:
-- Used by the finance and growth teams for quarterly reporting and ROI checks.
-- Can be filtered to a specific year or quarter (e.g., LIKE '%2025%').
--
-- NOTES:
-- - The FTD logic uses `QUALIFY ROW_NUMBER() = 1` to find first-time payers
-- - All revenue is filtered to `is_paid = 1` and `refunded = false`
-- - This version does not include revenue aggregation (only counts)
-- - Custom quarter format: 'Q1_2025', 'Q2_2025', etc.
-- ==============================================================================


with MARKETING as (SELECT
CASE
-- Q1 (August, September, October)
WHEN MONTH(date) IN (8, 9, 10) AND YEAR(date) >= 2019 THEN CONCAT('Q1_', YEAR(date) + 1)

-- Q2 (November, December, January)
WHEN MONTH(date) IN (11, 12) AND YEAR(date) >= 2019 THEN CONCAT('Q2_', YEAR(date) + 1)
WHEN MONTH(date) = 1 AND YEAR(date) >= 2021 THEN CONCAT('Q2_', YEAR(date))

-- Q3 (February, March, April)
WHEN MONTH(date) IN (2, 3, 4) AND YEAR(date) >= 2020 THEN CONCAT('Q3_', YEAR(date))

-- Q4 (May, June, July)
WHEN MONTH(date) IN (5, 6, 7) AND YEAR(date) >= 2020 THEN CONCAT('Q4_', YEAR(date))

ELSE 'Other' -- Optional: Handle other dates if necessary
END AS custom_quarter
, sum(cost) as marketing_spend

FROM
GURUSHOTS.MARKETING3.APPSFLYER_XPEND_DATA
group by 1),


payings as
(select CASE
-- Q1 (August, September, October)
WHEN MONTH(date_paid::DATE) IN (8, 9, 10) AND YEAR(date_paid::DATE) >= 2019 THEN CONCAT('Q1_', YEAR(date_paid::DATE) + 1)

-- Q2 (November, December, January)
WHEN MONTH(date_paid::DATE) IN (11, 12) AND YEAR(date_paid::DATE) >= 2019 THEN CONCAT('Q2_', YEAR(date_paid::DATE) + 1)
WHEN MONTH(date_paid::DATE) = 1 AND YEAR(date_paid::DATE) >= 2021 THEN CONCAT('Q2_', YEAR(date_paid::DATE))

-- Q3 (February, March, April)
WHEN MONTH(date_paid::DATE) IN (2, 3, 4) AND YEAR(date_paid::DATE) >= 2020 THEN CONCAT('Q3_', YEAR(date_paid::DATE))

-- Q4 (May, June, July)
WHEN MONTH(date_paid::DATE) IN (5, 6, 7) AND YEAR(date_paid::DATE) >= 2020 THEN CONCAT('Q4_', YEAR(date_paid::DATE))

ELSE 'Other' -- Optional: Handle other dates if necessary
END AS custom_quarter, count(distinct member_id) AS payers
from PC_FIVETRAN_DB.MAIN2_APPLICATION_PRODUCTION.PAYMENTS
where refunded = FALSE and is_paid = 1
GROUP BY 1),
